Title: Make the order of 'Add rule' buttons more user friendly
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 2.2.0b1
Date: 1647861128
Class: feature

On ruleset pages users may add a rule by clicking buttons of different context information. These
buttons are now sorted with respect to their relevance for users. The new order is

* Add rule
* Add rule for current host (and service/device, if available)
* Add rule in folder `<folder_name>`
